## DeepSeek V4 Flash Free validation fallback

If full validation is too slow or the free model/session is unstable, validate in this order and stop at the first real failure:

```bash
make safety-scan
```

```bash
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
python -m ruff check app tests
```

```bash
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
python -B -m pytest -q
```

```bash
cd frontend
source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh
nvm use 20
npm test
npm run build
```

Treat these as non-blocking if final summaries pass:

```text
- passlib crypt deprecation warning from dependency
- React act(...) warnings in existing hook tests
- intentional ErrorBoundary test Error: fail
```

